">with</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#B392F0\"> wait</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">: </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">true</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> to retrieve the result. If it still shows running, stop there for </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">this</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> response. Leave same</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">-</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">scope work </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">with</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> the agent </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">while</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> it runs.</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">255497</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">*</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\"> Use read_agent for completed background agents, not to check whether they</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">'re done.</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B31D28;--shiki-light-font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#FDAEB7;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic\">`</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">255498</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">        : </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">\"\"</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8\">,</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">255499</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">    Y</