><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">255506</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">* Typical workflow: start agent (background) </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">\\u2192</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> wait for completion notification </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">\\u2192</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> read_agent (get result) </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">\\u2192</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> write_agent (send refinement) </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">\\u2192</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> wait for notification </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">\\u2192</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> read_agent (get updated result).</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">255507</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">* Use read_agent with since_turn to get only new responses without re-reading earlier turns.</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line line--hit\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">255508</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">* Idle agents (status: \"idle\") are waiting for messages </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">\\u2014</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\"> they're ready to receive write_agent immediately.`</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">255509</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F97583\">        :</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dar